{
  "stem": "894.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never found out who did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, of course, you couldn't blame anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't-- were not aware, you know, of doing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I had a mark here for a very long time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we arrived to the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they had-- like, in an open field, they had set up tents, not barracks like they had there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was tents and a whole different life started for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were much more tolerant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, we-- the-- we had the rules, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had-- we had a fence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You couldn't just come and go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You-- you were fenced in in barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you had the tower that looked down and made sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But the barbed wire was not electrified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that if somebody really made an effort, you could pry it apart-- which I found out later at one point that you can do that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And what they did-- they give us much more food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They talked to us much better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You didn't feel that you were threatened by death every moment of the day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had a factory, a munition factory, a large munition factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had tracks right outside of the tents that took trains where, I suppose, they, you know, picked up the ammunition.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there we were introduced to this factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to work 12 hours a day or 12 hours a night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One week it was daytime, one week it was in the nighttime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we went to work, like I said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That slap in Auschwitz taught me that I am not trying to get out of anything, whatever I have to do, as long as I'm there.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
